<h1>build</h1>
<p>
<b>Requirements</b>: valac &ge; 0.11.5, clutter-1.0 and json-glib-1.0</p>
<p>
Type <code>make</code> to build rubik then <code>./rubik</code> to launch the game.<br />
Installation is not currently well supported, thus discouraged.
</p>

<h1>usage</h1>
<p>Run <code>./rubik</code> to launch the game</p>
<p>
<ul>
<li>&rarr; to rotate a cube slice click on a face and move the mouse</li>
<li>&rarr; to rotate the view either right click, click outside the cube or keep SHIFT pressed</li>
<li>&rarr; to rotate the cube around itself press either `a', `q', `w', `e', `d'  or `s'</li>
<li>&rarr; press ESC to reset rotation</li>
</ul>
</p>
